&lt;li&gt;Design scalable solution approaches using Trolley’s APIs, SDKs, widgets, embedded onboarding flows, app integrations, and automation capabilities.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Help customers evaluate implementation options based on their internal resources, timelines, and desired recipient experience.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Translate business requirements into technical solution designs, integration recommendations, and phased rollout plans.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Advise on data flows, authentication, configuration, implementation sequencing, and long-term maintainability.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
